{"name":"Proxomo Software","permalink":"proxomo-software","crunchbase_url":"http://www.crunchbase.com/company/proxomo-software","homepage_url":"http://www.proxomo.com","blog_url":"http://blog.proxomo.com","blog_feed_url":"feed://blog.proxomo.com/feed/","twitter_username":"proxomo","category_code":"mobile","number_of_employees":null,"founded_year":2010,"founded_month":4,"founded_day":null,"deadpooled_year":null,"deadpooled_month":null,"deadpooled_day":null,"deadpooled_url":null,"tag_list":"backend-as-a-service, baas, mbaas, smartfeatures, autoscheduler, android, iphone, windows-phone","alias_list":null,"email_address":"info@proxomo.com","phone_number":"","description":"Intel for mobile apps!","created_at":"Fri Sep 09 01:11:52 UTC 2011","updated_at":"Thu Oct 25 03:30:46 UTC 2012","overview":"<p>Proxomo is a backend as a service cloud backend technology company in the emerging market for context brokerage services.</p>\n\n<p>Proxomo enables web and mobile innovators to build feature rich, highly scalable, ultra secure apps radically faster.</p>\n\n<p>It was named one of Gartner Group&#8217;s six &#8220;Cool Vendors in Context-Aware Computing&#8221;.</p>\n\n<p>Proxomo provides a RESTful API that cross integrates a variety of context services designed to simplify the development of context-aware applications, including location, collaboration (both e-mail and SMS) and social networking. Proxomo functions as an abstraction layer, shielding developers from the complexity involved in directly integrating a variety of context agents, while simultaneously enriching the services it provides with additional functionality (such as application data storage, centralized user profile authentication and management, and user events).</p>","image":{"available_sizes":[[[150,29],"assets/images/resized/0015/5183/155183v2-max-150x150.png"],[[250,48],"assets/images/resized/0015/5183/155183v2-max-250x250.png"],[[300,58],"assets/images/resized/0015/5183/155183v2-max-450x450.png"]],"attributi